metadata.description:
A song about getting too high and overthinking my music career! Just drop the songs damn it! 

Written by DEEGAN
Produced by DEEGAN & Kilo Sweeney


Lyrics:
I ain’t tryna get lost in the promo
Talk about the type of man who a no show 
Living large yet I’m feelin so slow mo
I’m feelin hot like I’m slipping in the ozone 
I don’t wanna live my life through a tv
Give up everything just to be on repeat
Tell ‘em anything just so they can see me
Copy everything just to be how he be
Phantom on a bitch
Ima go phantom on a bitch
I need fans to make me rich
But I need bands to make me rich 
Typa pressure make a man get up and leave
Pressure had me scared I couldn’t breathe
Pressure make fool right out of me
I was somewhere I could never see

Ride longstyle like it’s limousine 
Heart pumpin pumpin like some creatine 
Smokin god damn trippin off the green
Paranoia had ya boilin off the heat I seen

I been huffin cigs out the corner store
I been off the shits outya modum bro
I been makin stacks what’s the motive bro
I cant believe you let the money do the dosie doe

I ain’t tryna get lost in the promo
Talk about the type of man who a no show 
Living large yet I’m feelin so slow mo
I’m feelin hot like I’m slipping in the ozone 
I don’t wanna live my life through a tv
Give up everything just to be on repeat
Tell ‘em anything just so they can see me
Copy everything just to be how he be

I rock 
I roll

Trippin out think I made my mama too worried 
Hear me out I was hittin pounds in a hurry 
Cry a lot just get the trial and the jury 

Trippin out think I made my mama too worried 
Hear me out I was hittin pounds in a hurry 
Cry a lot just get the trial and the jury 

I know
You’re Something special 
I know you want me to
Something special 
I know you want me to
You’re Something special
